{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 This example shows how to fetch a list of the files in a specific directory, using the \cf2 FileListGet() \cf1 function.\par
\par
Zoom from Directory Name to select a directory, and set the filter and option to return subdirectories. Then press Start.\par
\par
The file list will be returned into a vector, then scanned and displayed in a table.\par
